test.description:
`test` lets you use search.maven.org from command line.
Example: `test hibernate` will search for artifacts with hibernate in its name.
You can use any of the search modifiers search.maven.org supports, i.e.:
`test c:QuarkusTest` will search for artifacts with class `QuarkusTest`

rollingupgrade.description: `rollingupgrade` lets you test an in place rolling upgrade of `Infinispan` servers with two different versions.
